xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.49.0
-------------------------------
Released August 2025



xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.49~rc1
---------------------------------
Released August 2025
* Add new (rust based) account portal implementation
* Add new (rust based) app chooser portal implementation
* Issues fixed:
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/guidog/xdg-desktop-portal-phosh/-/issues/9
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/guidog/xdg-desktop-portal-phosh/-/issues/10
* Contributors:
    * Arun Mani J
    * Guido Günther

xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.48.0
-------------------------------
Released June 2025
* Update to pfs 0.0.4 to fix the empty state when the initially
  opened directory is empty
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther

xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.47.0
-------------------------------
Released May 2025
* notification-portal: Handle cellbroadcast categories
* Update to pfs 0.0.3
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther

xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.46.0
-------------------------------
Released March 2025
* Add notification portal with initial v2 support. This allows notification
  features like categories (`im.received`) or body markup in flatpaks
  to be delivered to the user.
* Support setting lockscreen wallpaper
* Update to pfs 0.0.2 so support search and other improvements
* Contributors:
    * Gotam Gorabh
    * Guido Günther

xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.45.0
-------------------------------
Released February 2025
* Use GTK 4.17's portal avoidance
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther

xdg-desktop-portal-phosh 0.44.0
-------------------------------
Released December 2024
* New experimental adaptive file chooser portal
* Use 'phosh' as portal name rather than 'pmp'
* Contributors:
    * Guido Günther

